2025-04-07FIN, GACCustoms TariffUnited States Surtax Order (Motor Vehicles 2025)UNITED STATES SURTAX ORDER (MOTOR VEHICLES 2025) in order to establish reciprocal surtaxes of 25% on passenger vehicles and certain trucks that originate in the United States in accordance with the Determination of Country of Origin for the purpose of Marking Goods Regulations, covering approximately a total of $35.6 billion in annual imports.N/A
subject: United States Surtax Order (Motor Vehicles 2025)
precis: UNITED STATES SURTAX ORDER (MOTOR VEHICLES 2025) in order to establish reciprocal surtaxes of 25% on passenger vehicles and certain trucks that originate in the United States in accordance with the Determination of Country of Origin for the purpose of Marking Goods Regulations, covering approximately a total of $35.6 billion in annual imports.
